longBusinessSummary: Fremont Gold Ltd., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in the United States. It primarily explores for gold properties. The company's flagship project is the Griffon gold project, which consists of 179 claims covering an area of 15 square kilometers located in White Pine County, Nevada. The company was formerly known as Palisades Ventures Inc. and changed its name to Fremont Gold Ltd. in June 2017. Fremont Gold Ltd. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
